{
  "text": "where Q, Q \u2032 ,Q are zeroth-order terms. Here W t denotes the transposed of W and W * stands for W t . No first order terms appear in [CITATION_1] , (21) and (22), giving as a result a Schr\u00f6dinger-type equation. Mind",
